    <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Book of prayers in memory of the Prophet Muḥammad (f. 1v-71v) followed by a section with names of the companions (asmāʼ al-ṣaḥābah) (f. 72v-86v).</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
